---
import Tech from './Tech.astro';
---

<section id="about" class="scroll-mt-8 border-t border-neutral-200 py-16" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
  <h2 id="about-heading" class="section-label">About</h2>
  <div class="mt-8 grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-2">
    <div class="space-y-4 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        I'm a software engineer based in Sydney. Most of my time goes into backend work: Node.js
        and TypeScript services, data modelling in PostgreSQL and MongoDB, and infrastructure on
        Google Cloud.
      </p>
      <p>
        Lately, that time has gone into <a href="https://uplerr.com" class="link-quiet">Uplerr</a>,
        an AI-powered job-search platform that's live today. It comes from a simple conviction: job
        seekers deserve to know exactly where they stand before they apply.
      </p>
      <p>
        I approach software from the user's side of the screen first. The engineering exists to
        serve the product, which is also why I care about leaving code cleaner than I found it.
      </p>
    </div>
    <dl class="space-y-5 text-sm md:pl-10">
      <div>
        <dt class="meta-label">Now</dt>
        <dd class="mt-1.5 leading-relaxed text-neutral-700">
          Working and building. Uplerr is live; I'm shaping what it becomes next.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt class="meta-label">Learning</dt>
        <dd class="mt-1.5 leading-relaxed text-neutral-700">
          System design that stays simple as it grows, and <Tech name="Go" size={18} />.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt class="meta-label">Care about</dt>
        <dd class="mt-1.5 leading-relaxed text-neutral-700">
          Efficient, scalable software that people actually enjoy using.
        </dd>
      </div>
    </dl>
  </div>
</section>
